Two Cents (If You&rsquo;re Still Alive to Pay)</h2>\n\n<div class=\"leaderboard\">\n  <strong>&#9733; TERRITORY GAINS THIS WEEK &#9733;</strong>\n  Donald Trump &nbsp;&nbsp; +37<br>\n  Cokro &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; +11<br>\n  Blood Captain &nbsp; +10<br>\n  Wu-Tang &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; +5<br>\n  busfat &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; +1<br>\n  Brimex &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; +1\n</div>\n\n<hr>\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"640\" height=\"220\" style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;background:#0a0800;display:block;margin:18px auto\">\n<text x=\"320\" y=\"22\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" letter-spacing=\"2\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">TERRITORY GAINS THIS WEEK</text>\n<line x1=\"20\" y1=\"28\" x2=\"620\" y2=\"28\" stroke=\"#3a2a00\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"48\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Donald Trump</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"35\" width=\"400\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"566\" y=\"48\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+37</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"76\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Cokro</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"63\" width=\"118\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"284\" y=\"76\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+11</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"104\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Blood Captain</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"91\" width=\"108\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"274\" y=\"104\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+10</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"132\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Wu-Tang</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"119\" width=\"54\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"220\" y=\"132\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+5</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"160\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">busfat</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"147\" width=\"10\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"176\" y=\"160\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+1</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"188\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Brimex</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"175\" width=\"10\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"176\" y=\"188\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">+1</text>\n</svg>\n\n\n<h3>The Golden Emperor Marches On — Three Headquarters Smashed, Two Bosses Erased!</h3>\n<span class=\"subhead\">Trump Adds Thirty-Seven Turfs to His Gilded Empire While the Weak Are Ground to Dust Beneath His Heel</span>\n<span class=\"byline\">By Our Man in the Trenches, Ignatius P. Flambeau</span>\n\n<p>Good Lord Almighty and all the saints that ever drew breath — <strong>Donald Trump</strong>, the Platinum Pompadour of Vendetta City, the Golden Emperor of every block, alley, and dockside dive worth a plugged nickel, has done it <em>again.</em> Faithful readers, you will recall from last week's breathless dispatch that this man had just finished dismembering the wretched Lakhhe in the most systematic fashion this city has witnessed in living memory. Six headquarters captured. Six! We assumed, naively, that the man might rest. We assumed wrong.</p>\n\n<p>Between April 27th and the ink-black evening of May 4th, Trump stormed two more headquarters — those belonging to the forgettable <strong>fdgdfdfgdf</strong> on the 28th and the luckless <strong>Strix</strong> on May 2nd — before their outfits collapsed entirely and vanished from the rolls of Vendetta City's living concerns. Both men are gone. Both empires, dust. Trump, meanwhile, has added a staggering <strong>thirty-seven turfs</strong> to his dominion and grown his already-terrifying garrison to <strong>5,172 souls</strong> — up another 147 units this week alone. The man is not merely conquering. He is <em>building a standing army.</em> Citizens, be advised: when a man fortifies at that pace, he is not done fighting. He has barely begun.</p>\n\n<p>And lest anyone suppose the Emperor spends all his hours in pure territorial conquest, let the record show that Trump's raiders descended upon <strong>Blood Captain's</strong> coffers with such precision that they stripped away the maximum haul in a single stroke — five hundred dollars cash and five hundred arms, clean as a whistle. The Golden Emperor, it appears, does not merely want your streets. He wants your wallet too.</p>\n\n<hr>\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"640\" height=\"192\" style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;background:#0a0800;display:block;margin:18px auto\">\n<text x=\"320\" y=\"22\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" letter-spacing=\"2\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">HEAVIEST LOSSES THIS WEEK</text>\n<line x1=\"20\" y1=\"28\" x2=\"620\" y2=\"28\" stroke=\"#3a2a00\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"48\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Way6444</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"35\" width=\"400\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"566\" y=\"48\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">-9</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"76\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">FIFTH BLOOD EMPEROR</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"63\" width=\"222\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"388\" y=\"76\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">-5</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"104\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Strix</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"91\" width=\"133\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"299\" y=\"104\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">-3</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"132\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Thunder Sov</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"119\" width=\"44\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"210\" y=\"132\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">-1</text>\n<text x=\"154\" y=\"160\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">fdgdfdfgdf</text>\n<rect x=\"160\" y=\"147\" width=\"44\" height=\"16\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" opacity=\"0.85\"/>\n<text x=\"210\" y=\"160\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">-1</text>\n</svg>\n\n\n<h3>Blood Captain — The Busiest Cutthroat in the City!</h3>\n<span class=\"subhead\">Twenty-Two Raids and Ten Captures in a Single Week — But His Gangsters Are Paying the Price</span>\n<span class=\"byline\">By Our Man in the Trenches, Ignatius P. Flambeau</span>\n\n<p>If Donald Trump is the Emperor of Vendetta City, then <strong>Blood Captain</strong> — who we shall henceforth call <em>the Scarlet Privateer</em> — is its most tireless buccaneer. This week, the Scarlet Privateer unleashed a positively exhausting campaign of violence: <strong>twenty-two raids</strong> plundering cash and weapons from rivals across the map, and <strong>ten territorial captures</strong> that netted him a net gain of ten freshly branded turfs. He even found time to smash <strong>Thunder Sov's</strong> headquarters into splinters on the 28th, sending that poor wretch into oblivion alongside fdgdfdfgdf and Strix.</p>\n\n<p>Three bosses eliminated in one week, readers. <em>Three.</em> It is enough to make a man check the locks on his own front door.</p>\n\n<p>And yet — and here is the cruel irony that our correspondent cannot help but savour — the Scarlet Privateer's own garrison has shrunk by <strong>127 units</strong> this week. His henchmen and bouncers have been paying in blood for every block seized. One does not launch twenty-two raids and ten captures without casualties. Blood Captain is gaining ground, yes, but his boys are dying to take it. The question Vendetta City is now whispering in its back rooms and speakeasies is this: how long can the Privateer sustain such furious losses before the ledger comes due?</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h3>Wu-Tang Fortifies — The Iron Fist Sharpens His Claws</h3>\n<span class=\"subhead\">Five New Turfs and One Hundred and Sixty Fresh Recruits Signal Serious Ambition on the East\n<hr>\n<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"640\" height=\"114\" style=\"font-family:Georgia,serif;background:#0a0800;display:block;margin:18px auto\">\n<text x=\"320\" y=\"22\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#c8a84a\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"bold\" letter-spacing=\"2\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">HQ RAIDS — TOP ATTACKERS</text>\n<line x1=\"20\" y1=\"30\" x2=\"620\" y2=\"30\" stroke=\"#3a2a00\" stroke-width=\"1\"/>\n<text x=\"148\" y=\"53\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Donald Trump</text>\n<polygon points=\"156,43 161,48 156,53 151,48\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\"/>\n<rect x=\"170\" y=\"41\" width=\"410\" height=\"14\" fill=\"#6b1010\" opacity=\"0.9\" rx=\"1\"/>\n<rect x=\"577\" y=\"41\" width=\"3\" height=\"14\" fill=\"#c03030\"/>\n<text x=\"588\" y=\"53\" fill=\"#c04040\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">2✕</text>\n<text x=\"148\" y=\"82\" text-anchor=\"end\" fill=\"#a09060\" font-size=\"11\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">Blood Captain</text>\n<polygon points=\"156,72 161,77 156,82 151,77\" fill=\"#8b1a1a\"/>\n<rect x=\"170\" y=\"70\" width=\"205\" height=\"14\" fill=\"#6b1010\" opacity=\"0.9\" rx=\"1\"/>\n<rect x=\"372\" y=\"70\" width=\"3\" height=\"14\" fill=\"#c03030\"/>\n<text x=\"383\" y=\"82\" fill=\"#c04040\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" font-family=\"Georgia,serif\">1✕</text>\n</svg>","stats":{"total_tiles_start":21466,"total_tiles_end":21512,"hq_captures":3,"raids":46,"pure_captures":15,"capture_and_raids":4,"pure_raids":27,"total_cash_looted":4029.7,"newcomers":1,"vanished":3,"top_gainer":"Donald Trump","top_gainer_net":37}}